  "2026-07-21T07:33:05.774Z",codex-root-20260721,"Progress evidence: decomposed both suppressed cli-bootstrap functions below cognitive complexity 16, pruned two suppressions, and ratcheted the repository maximum from 154 to 152. This advances but does not complete the broader 76-suppression burn-down item."
